name: Jump Higher
description:
This is my unposted work, which i captured in Port of Tanjung Emas, Semarang, Jawa Tengah, Indonesia. 

At that time I saw children playing on a ship that was anchored, and they jumped from the ship into the water. That's an interesting moment i thought, so I captured it.

Semarang, 27 August 2016.
